br />\n果邊做野？定讀書</blockquote><br />\n我3年前都係WH黎  果時WH一期仲係得125個位<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊野</blockquote><br />\n香港好似好少人申請，果邊生活如何？<br />\n如何可以我都想留幾年</blockquote><br />\n你黎到穩定到先算啦 <br />\n識大把話要留幾年  最尾一年唔夠就走人<br />\n<br />\n識挪威 中東 紐西蘭朋友 英文係native  番緊日本語學校<br />\n想搵做廚房都有難度  挪威果個而家都係洗緊碗<br />\n所以我勸你有日文個底先出發</blockquote><br />\n我打算搵左工先過去，我做開果d廚房對比地係外國容易d搵工，不過網上日本working holiday的資訊比較少，所以開post問問"},{"pid":"4763606b92a1c67cc96e394e00ff06e7f20c7694","tid":265561,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b2b2417ae239a0bceb41cde51aa5d7e8fe5684","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大阪生活3年路過  工作中~</blockquote><br />\n果邊做野？定讀書</blockquote><br />\n我3年前都係WH黎  果時WH一期仲係得125個位<br />\n<br />\n而家做緊野</blockquote><br />\n香港好似好少人申請，果邊生活如何？<br />\n如何可以我都想留幾年</blockquote><br />\n你黎到穩定到先算啦 <br />\n識大把話要留幾年  最尾一年唔夠就走人<br />\n<br />\n識挪威 中東 紐西蘭朋友 英文係native  番緊日本語學校<br />\n想搵做廚房都有難度  挪威果個而家都係洗緊碗<br />\n所以我勸你有日文個底先出發</blockquote><br />\n我打算搵左工先過去，我做開果d廚房對比地係外國容易d搵工，不過網上日本working holiday的資訊比較少，所以開post問問</blockquote><br />\n你有門路先搵工後到步就無問題啦"},{"pid":"8c912aeeb77fe9cfb5de5aab311766dc22f87f7a","tid":265561,"uid":21633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗"},{"pid":"769d8460cf1b9df952e94203896955025d8cae39","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d人銀彈充足過黎頭半年都唔做野剩係玩既"},{"pid":"8ae24e7793b2294520399747bb3e35a1cc1d445e","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n每個地方都有差既一面同缺點  睇你接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f62276392a8866e54bcdf2fd2fb9dced0af308","tid":265561,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:52:30.000Z","msg":"等緊結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8b99791afef7dd4073cddfe3e2fdfc6b71a48a","tid":265561,"uid":21633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n每個地方都有差既一面同缺點  睇你接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只可以講香港唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企係日本做咗幾十年野都頂唔順個垃圾日本政府而家準備走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e516b75c48b271cf9d3d10a173828c983855bebf","tid":265561,"uid":8584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:54:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你喺香港咪又係奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd97358ed5ce3a15d7eabe7c90336eb9cec633b","tid":265561,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你喺香港咪又係奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時有話我響香港？<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3eb16c20f144d04582d23c3a993b56f1479e4c","tid":265561,"uid":107298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n去一年睇下人地個國家，深入了解下，見識下姐，冇得咁比較<br />\nd日本人一樣會黎香港working holiday，因為唔係佢地自己國家，會覺得好多野好有趣，選擇留耐d 了解下，就算佢地發現有好多缺點"},{"pid":"4fd6bcd6e693be77fad8a85d8d0dede33e3fad27","tid":265561,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你喺香港咪又係奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時有話我響香港？<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667927f7a36b4faabf70725d5591d85b699ead2a","tid":265561,"uid":107298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外勞就外勞啦<br />\nHol 咩iday<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你喺香港咪又係奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時有話我響香港？<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每個人想要的野唔同，你唔鐘意呢種旅遊／工作方式冇需要入黎<br />\n大把北歐國家的人會鐘意去其他國家生活，感受唔同文化，就算人地國家好富裕都好<br />\n外勞咪外勞囉，最鐘要自已開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a9ccdbc51724397b449df78bd3ae88d89049b","tid":265561,"uid":89137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"申請左，好擔心結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a284e844df3ab5607c3a64dace06ead41fabe6bb","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n每個地方都有差既一面同缺點  睇你接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只可以講香港唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企係日本做咗幾十年野都頂唔順個垃圾日本政府而家準備走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同女朋友就喜歡日本多d  對我地黎講香港好差下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c4d6873b8ea35852194e51826727e66e5405fb","tid":265561,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:15:41.000Z","msg":"諗住今年第二期申請"},{"pid":"2763aebe04eb15533823a42161be9c0b30531f3d","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住今年第二期申請</blockquote><br />\n仲有時間咪學定日文先~"},{"pid":"03d998a59c27da4abc99482a6513394cc49fa6f7","tid":265561,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗住今年第二期申請</blockquote><br />\n仲有時間咪學定日文先~</blockquote><br />\n重拾緊，上年考左N4"},{"pid":"fdebfaaa1b7d00cb111ba9b9efdb9e977c633d7d","tid":265561,"uid":21633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n去一年睇下人地個國家，深入了解下，見識下姐，冇得咁比較<br />\nd日本人一樣會黎香港working holiday，因為唔係佢地自己國家，會覺得好多野好有趣，選擇留耐d 了解下，就算佢地發現有好多缺點</blockquote><br />\n至少做咗少少準備先去了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見你日文都唔識驚你去度比日本民族主義恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n否則你最後都係會浪費咗時間因爲溝通其實好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去見識唔係無問題不過至少準備下先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由其你係去wh唔係去旅遊"},{"pid":"506ec5427a5806cd382f13c9a0a508f044b278ce","tid":265561,"uid":21633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得住個度同係個度讀書既人先知日本發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企有曰本永住   我就覺得太垃圾取消咗</blockquote><br />\n每個地方都有差既一面同缺點  睇你接唔接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只可以講香港唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企係日本做咗幾十年野都頂唔順個垃圾日本政府而家準備走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同女朋友就喜歡日本多d  對我地黎講香港好差下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食野真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過住既話d税勁到痴線<br />\n賺埋都唔夠比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6912388d5273cf15b08d8f0d25f6960e0139e7","tid":265561,"uid":107298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:33:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>申請左，好擔心結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有少少，想知你計劃書點寫？"},{"pid":"84d3a58249846359573a566dffbedbc1cb34765e","tid":265561,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實日本除咗旅遊之外真係好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg